  },
  "universal_guidelines": [
    "Use 'Manrope' for all headings to give a technical, precision feel.",
    "Use 'IBM Plex Sans' for body text for maximum legibility.",
    "Primary Action Color is #0066CC (Dimeda Blue).",
    "Critical/Warning Color is #FA4616 (Medirol Orange).",
    "Always include a 'Scan Serial Number' button in the main navigation or dashboard.",
    "Forms must be broken into small steps (Wizard pattern) to avoid overwhelming technicians.",
    "Use the specific Medirol product images provided in 'image_assets' to ensure authenticity.",
    "All interactive elements must have `data-testid` attributes.",
    "Do not use gradients for backgrounds; use subtle noise or flat colors for a clinical look.",
    "Ensure high contrast (WCAG AA) for all text, especially in the 'Dark Mode' variant."
  ],
  "instructions_to_main_agent": "You are building the frontend for the Dimeda Service App. Use the provided JSON data to style your components. Focus on the 'Service Wizard' and 'Dashboard' views. Use the real product images for the 'Product Details' section. Implement a 'Dark Mode' toggle as technicians may work in low-light environments."
}